init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He came upon a beautiful ring and fell in love with it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Before he could propose, the woman left him to marry another man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decided to use his shapeshifting ability to switch places with the groom at the altar.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Over the years, he had grown into a real playboy and had left his true love for another.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She went to her husband and told him about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Her husband said, “no it’s just play.”
